  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Warning this do not means you would be able to easily do the \"render on server, cancel first query\" Because rendering on server would not make the facets value clickable. They would not yet be binded.\n\nI believe if one use would really want to implement a full server-side - bind on frontend, it would require us to work on #833 a lot more.\n",
