    "body": "> > An event would be way better indeed\n> > Why/How would it be better?\n\nI think it's better because it allows you to add different hooks from different places, and setting a hook by using events means you're not replacing someone else's hook! (which is the case if you have to do `thing.beforeHook = ...`)\n",
