  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "In the end, for a start, I will go for the initial proposal that can solve the needs and do not require too much new API entries.\n\nIf you really need to split your hook in multiple functions that will be still feasible, on your side. Using any middleware library or your own.\n\nWe will see how people use this and iterate if needed.\n\nExposing a single function should be ok in most cases.\n",
